        <h1>What Atalanta Systems does</h1>
        <img src="83.jpg" alt="1000 Lakeside" width="350" height="234" class="wrap-right"/>
      <p>Atalanta Systems is a specialist IT solutions provider, specialising in using open source technology to streamline corporate IT 		  	infrastructure.</p>

	<p>Having built a network of bright and experienced associates with skills spanning UNIX, Linux, Windows, networking, security, web
	development and web design, we create bespoke teams of specialists, providing a multi-disciplinary approach, to deliver a holistic solution 
	to any problem you throw at us. </p>

	<p>Atalanta Systems uses agile methodologies throughout - we'll agree the simplest, smallest outcome that will bring the 		greatest business benefit to your company, and work on that first - keeping your costs down, and making sure we're always adding value.</p>

	<p>We believe in using technology and talent to add value to your business - by making your systems faster and more reliable, and by allowing 		your technical staff to focus on work that really matters and that moves your business forward.</p>

	<p>We sit comfortably on the borders between business, management and technology.  Coming from a professional, corporate background, we understand customers, their business needs and process, their client-facing requirements, as well as the details of their technical infrastructure - a rare-breed combination of technical and business acumen.

	<p>Put simply - we will work with you to streamline your technology, to bring you tangible business benefits.</p>
      
	<p>Find out more about <a href="services.html">our services</a>.</p>	
	
